Comparison of Datasets

Comparing the GM24385_2020.09 and GM24385_2020.11 Releases

Throughput

The cumulative yield is calculated from the sequencing summary created by MinKNOW during the course of the experiment. The figures here include both QC pass and fail reads, they are calculated from the length of basecalls.

Read Accuracy

The accuracy of reads is calculated using the stats_from_bam program from pomoxis, after alignment to the reference sequence using minimap2 with the -x ont preset. Depicted are reads alignments to chr1 only of the human reference.

Read length

The length of reads is calculated from MinKNOW's sequencing summary. The figures here include both QC pass and fail reads, they are calculated from the length of basecalls.
